/game8.jp/dragalialost/233911\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame8.jp%2Fdragalialost%2F233911&d=8BteI%2Bf9ky9hy%2B9tl%2BrAfcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=5c6e528c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://game8.jp/dragalialost/233911</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A:<br />\n刷幾隻角，龍先開得？<br />\n你有一角一龍都可以開，有人刷幾日都未有<br />\n<br />\n要做啲乜？<br />\n打主線，副本<br />\n<br />\n同人合作打有幾多石？<br />\n50石一個人，最多2500石<br />\n<br />\n點升戰力？<br />\n升lvl<br />\n升環<br />\n龍<br />\n造武<br />\n建築<br />\n卡<br />\n<br />\n點有多啲瑪那？<br />\n打主線，錢關<br />\n課金<br />\n<br />\n點造高星武？<br />\n升建築lvl再升主城同鍛造<br />\n<br />\n唔夠錢點算？<br />\n打錢關<br />\n<br />\n資源唔夠？<br />\n諗定:<br />\n升咩角色先<br />\n武器玩3星3段屬性定4星2段<br />\n<br />\n爆發攻擊(蓄力)可以破盾，也可以大幅減少OD(技能槽)<br />\n<br />\n紅色預警圈可以使用技能無敵幀擋住，紫色的不行<br />\n昏迷&mdash;&mdash;受到攻擊後方可解除<br />\n黑暗&mdash;&mdash;命中率下降<br />\n濕身&mdash;&mdash;必被暴擊<br />\n冰凍&mdash;&mdash;被同伴攻擊後可解除"},{"pid":"dca6bf58c2ffa0af584b0c606565a2b174fc4f10","tid":847511,"uid":144943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T11:59:10.000Z","msg":"大家抽成點"},{"pid":"1c327fac98c83070fdccc0a184d56a08875a92d4","tid":847511,"uid":60765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:05:48.000Z","msg":"究竟開房下面個隨機組隊係已經公開左間房定係禁一下先係公開左間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41075999d851dbf371aa40124881f072f92dd412","tid":847511,"uid":3970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:08:56.000Z","msg":"抽中水龍<br />\n冇莉莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deeb6eefd93ff459201ce05dcf4324e246c349e4","tid":847511,"uid":146322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:28:39.000Z","msg":"升角色lv點升好慢"},{"pid":"319eaf340cd0ecae56db326042734c90d60b9d8a","tid":847511,"uid":142166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:47:21.000Z","msg":"我抽唔到五星龍得四星龍 但係有五星角同好多五